item.dc:creator: @Javacisnotrecognized _^_
item.description:
@Javacisnotrecognized wrote:

On most servers, it registers the account if someone else didn’t make it. Therefor all you have to do is log in. if you get “invalid username or password”, then the account is already taken and you choose a different name. If you can’t regiser the account, conact the owner about it.
